<text top="1929" left="231" width="791" height="62" font="font2" id="p1_t5" reading_order_no="6" segment_no="0" tag_type="text">that  the  system  is  useful  for  storytelling  [4].</text>
<text top="1980" left="280" width="919" height="63" font="font4" id="p1_t6" reading_order_no="7" segment_no="1" tag_type="text">The  Generic  Alice  tutorial  was  designed  around</text>
